Package: vlad
Type: Package
Title: Variable Life Adjusted Display
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
      person("Philipp", "Wittenberg", email = "pwitten@hsu-hh.de", role = 
      c("aut", "cre")),
      person("Sven", "Knoth", email = "<Sven.Knoth@gmx.de>", role = "aut"))
Depends: R (>= 2.10)
Maintainer: Philipp Wittenberg <pwitten@hsu-hh.de>
URL: https://github.com/wittenberg/vlad
BugReports: https://github.com/wittenberg/vlad/issues
Description: Contains functions to set up risk-adjusted quality control charts
    in health care. For the variable life adjusted display (VLAD) and RA-CUSUM
    based on log-likelihood ratio statistic parameters such as the Average Run
    Length (ARL) or control limits can be computed.
